channel.title: Someone please help!
channel.description:
hello, i've been trying to make a rsps for about some time now im pretty much done but theres just one problem. Every time i try to run the runserver.bat it tells me this.
"OVER was here ERROR: UNable to startup listener on port 43594- port already in use? config/options.cfg: files not found summoning:loading monsters from summon.cfg ... summoning: loaded 25 monsters from summon.cfg!"
I have source cheezscape and moparscape client and I've tried restarting my computer changing the port to something else I've even changed clients all said that the port was already in use
